### ─────────────────────────────
### DISHES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear plato (ADMIN)
### Requiere menu_type_id: obtenerlo desde GET /menu-types
POST {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Tarta de verdura",
  "description": "Tarta de verdura con queso y huevo",
  "menu_type_id": "126e0075-e8b4-4bd3-9f0f-41cdfa5aae0b"
}

###

### Listar todos los platos
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos paginados
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos filtrando por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos por tipo de menú
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?menu_type_id=126e0075-e8b4-4bd3-9f0f-41cdfa5aae0b
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener plato por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes/one?dishId={{dishId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar plato (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{dishId}}",
  "name": "Milanesa con puré de zapallo",
  "description": "Milanesa de carne con puré de zapallo",
  "menu_type_id": "126e0075-e8b4-4bd3-9f0f-41cdfa5aae0b",
  "active": true
}

###

### Eliminar plato (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{dishId}}"
}

###
